      • initialize

        protected void initialize​(net.dv8tion.jda.api.requests.RestAction<net.dv8tion.jda.api.entities.Message> action,
                          int pageNum)
        Description copied from class: Paginator
        Adds reactions to Paginator.

        If there is more than one page denoted by Paginator.MENU_PAGE_COUNT, then we add all reactions from Paginator.REACTIONS.
        If there is only one page in that list, we call Paginator.FINAL_ACTION and attempt to enter the submenu if one exists.

        Overrides:
        initialize in class Paginator
        Parameters:
        action - An action on a message. Usually a Message.editMessage(Message) action
        pageNum - The Page number (index number) of Paginator.EMBED_ARRAYLIST that the Paginator is currently showing
